cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI 

The paper discusses a new method for training feed forward neural networks, which is relevant to the sub-categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). The paper also briefly discusses the implications of the findings on the field of Deep Learning, which further supports the relevance to these sub-categories. Among these sub-categories, cs.NE and cs.LG are the most likely as they directly relate to the topic of neural network training and optimization.
